  "remarks": "\n Aleksandr ERMAKOV is or has been involved in relevant cyber activity, including being responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, malicious cyber activity that resulted in unauthorised access and exfiltration of sensitive data. The action compromised Medibank Private Limited, one of Australia’s largest private health insurance providers, and the resulting leak of millions of personal and medical records undermined the integrity, prosperity and security of Australia.\n",
